member.summary:
Gameplay-agnostic orchestration for 
style remote playback. It owns the  +
 pair and the extrapolation/starvation policy, so each demo
only has to: (1) decode an incoming push into a  and feed it via
, and (2) project + apply the sampled interpolation to its presentation.

Typical per-frame usage:

playback.Advance(deltaSeconds);
if (playback.TrySample(out var interpolation))
{
    var projected = project(in interpolation);
    presentation.Apply(in projected);
}
